info: Subprogram 2 of the Second Private Sector and Small and Medium-Sized Enterprises Development Program (PSME2) and the TA loan support the government's strategy to develop and promote small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) and undertake SME trade-related reforms to help achieve sustained and inclusive economic growth—a strategy embedded in the Seventh National Socio-Economic Development Plan (NSEDP7), 2011–2015.
name: SECOND PRIVATE SECTOR AND SME DEVELOPMENT PROGRAM-SUBPROGRAM 2
